on Jo Kyung Hee.

666
00:49:49,103 --> 00:49:51,368
The accident happened because
of the problem with the brake.

667
00:49:51,488 --> 00:49:53,734
A problem with the brake?

668
00:49:54,478 --> 00:49:55,849
