703
00:52:50,464 --> 00:52:51,910
Joo Ah Ran!

704
00:52:54,145 --> 00:52:55,872
Joo Seung.

705
00:53:11,190 --> 00:53:12,917
Did you really...

706
00:53:13,518 --> 00:53:15,039
